      <title>美国众议院通过对外援助计划中的新伊朗石油制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/new-iran-oil-sanctions-passed-by-us-house-in-foreign-aid-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院通过了针对伊朗石油行业的新制裁措施，该制裁措施将成为对外援助计划的一部分，该措施有望在几天内获得参议院通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/new-iran-oil-sanctions-passed-by-us-house-in-foreign-aid-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 剥离或禁止法案预计将在几天内成为美国法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-expected-to-become-us-law-within-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周六提出一项立法，迫使 TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动有限公司剥离其所有权股份，该法案很快就会成为法律，并将其与对乌克兰和以色列的一项重要援助计划挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-expected-to-become-us-law-within-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管存在全球风险，智利央行行长仍认为降息仍在轨道上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-central-bank-president-sees-rate-cuts-on-track-despite-global-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利央行行长罗莎娜·科斯塔(Rosanna Costa)表示，延长全球最大降息周期之一的计划保持不变，因为政策制定者已经将新的全球风险纳入其前景中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-central-bank-president-sees-rate-cuts-on-track-despite-global-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 16:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
